nodes.text: Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine 6 is the sixth and final issue of Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine. It was published by Titan Magazines on September 21, 2016.

Your adventure with the Force continues! Start your Jedi training within these very pages tackling the amazing puzzles and learning about the enemy, battles, alien species, and loads more! Don't miss the fantastic wall art and fantastic giveaways. You'll even receive your very own Jedi Training Certificate!
